{"tid":2509513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新教課書：人治不一定全是負面；教育局回應：未送審","createTime":"2021-04-29T13:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:10:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63926a4572ba4bc10c2faf7e839b591c995930c8","tid":2509513,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"公社科樣本書搶先送校 教育局：未送審<br />\n<br />\n九月新學年，高中課程中，「公民與社會發展科」會取代「通識教育科」，有出版社將最新編印的公社科樣本書送到學校，課本部分內容與現有通識科課本相似。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，有關參考教材未有按要求送審，對於有出版社將通識教育科坊間教材，以「公民與社會發展」科「課本」形式編印，局方深感遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588473-20210429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588473-20210429.htm&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=55dce06c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588473-20210429.htm&h=5ccffacf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588473-20210429.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公社科新書hard sell國民身份認同：人治不一定全是負面<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2508773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2508773</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/TB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwW7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=b2041c3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&h=27811555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/TB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI/</a>"}]}